      <title>阿布扎比 IHC 考虑回购，股价暴涨 43,000% 后降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/abu-dhabi-s-ihc-eyes-buyback-as-stock-cools-after-43-000-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际控股公司（International Holding Co.）是一家规模庞大的企业集团，由阿布扎比最有权势的王室成员之一担任主席，该公司计划实施 50 亿迪拉姆（14 亿美元）的回购计划，以在其股价 43,000% 的涨幅降温之际重振股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/abu-dhabi-s-ihc-eyes-buyback-as-stock-cools-after-43-000-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 04:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
